    "name": "Fisherman Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3179010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up for your fishing adventure across a chain of unique islands! Whether you're casting lines off the coast or hauling in the big catch deep at sea, you'll have plenty of tools to make every trip count.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/5498a2217240fae42ede64dd6de06814.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/5498a2217240fae42ede64dd6de06814.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/5498a2217240fae42ede64dd6de06814.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/1a351cbd5652773f5aaed074fbf1bb9f.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/1a351cbd5652773f5aaed074fbf1bb9f.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/1a351cbd5652773f5aaed074fbf1bb9f.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fishing Traps:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set it and forget it! Perfect for passive fishing while you explore or take on other tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/8ea12a1a2801afeb025c03861d82241a.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/8ea12a1a2801afeb025c03861d82241a.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/8ea12a1a2801afeb025c03861d82241a.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fishing Rods </strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casting Rod Equipped for accurate long-distance casting, these rods target larger fish species in deep seas. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/eb8d2bf17add7a89be977b9248dcdf7b.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/eb8d2bf17add7a89be977b9248dcdf7b.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/eb8d2bf17add7a89be977b9248dcdf7b.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><strong>Boats: </strong>From dinghies to decked-out deep-sea rides, your boat is your best buddy out on the water. Some are fast, some are sturdy, and some have room for a lot of fish. Upgrade them at Outposts to turn your humble hull into a fishing machine! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/2d5900be870e04cb8f9bcacc6e000464.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/2d5900be870e04cb8f9bcacc6e000464.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/2d5900be870e04cb8f9bcacc6e000464.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Outpost:</strong> Dock your boat and gear up! Upgrade your boats here to improve speed, storage, and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/a95cf30c1d79b0fa336c068b67b96880.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/a95cf30c1d79b0fa336c068b67b96880.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/a95cf30c1d79b0fa336c068b67b96880.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Shovel:</strong> Dig up upgrades or uncover hidden treasures. More useful than it looks!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/84ffc74a36eef7f658d87991ff246228.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/84ffc74a36eef7f658d87991ff246228.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/84ffc74a36eef7f658d87991ff246228.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Ultimate Fish Wagon: Your Reliable Catch Companion</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No fishing adventure is complete without a reliable way to transport your precious catch. Introducing the fishing wagon – an essential tool for transporting and storing your fish as you explore new waters and expand your fishing empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/7266c6a24923f3f3d920ffe5fd09dcf7.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/7266c6a24923f3f3d920ffe5fd09dcf7.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/7266c6a24923f3f3d920ffe5fd09dcf7.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Selling the Fish:</strong><br>Got fish? Turn those fins into funds! Wheel your haul into town, strike a deal, and watch your wallet grow. Save up for better rods, bigger boats, or just blow it all on a shiny new shovel—no judgment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/4b35d06797d4b1f19f1d84f35b012e66.poster.avif?t=1771006656\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/4b35d06797d4b1f19f1d84f35b012e66.webm?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179010/extras/4b35d06797d4b1f19f1d84f35b012e66.mp4?t=1771006656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
